ELK Ingestion Flow

WebSphere access logs are captured by Filebeat.

Filebeat parses the raw log line, extracts action and document ID, and sends the logs to Elasticsearch in daily indices.

Oracle CDC captures CMWS database changes from tables such as WORKFLOW_HISTORY and DOCUMENT_QUEUE.

